PartialRenderer
===============

PartialRenderer let's you to use view partials for displaying pagination.
Default generated partial's look is similar to those LinkRenderer renders


To install use command
./script/plugin install git://github.com/html/PartialRenderer.git partial_renderer

or 

git submodule add git://github.com/html/PartialRenderer.git vendor/plugins/partial_renderer/


and generate simple view partial

./script/generate partial_renderer go

Example
=======

./script/generate partial_renderer go

create  app/views/_pagination.haml

Now you have pagination like with WillPaginate::LinkRenderer, but you can change it's look and feel in your view partial

